{"tid":1383507,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線指揮官] 點樣進退好？","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:57:27.000Z","uid":264753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"532f0f096223b0a75e8979e955e9672db068390f","tid":1383507,"uid":264753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"琴晚喺上環發夢果陣，企喺中後排位置，留意住前排同⼿⾜<br />\n\r<br />\n旗⼿指示前進或者後退。但因為⼤家都開咗遮（加我⽣得短）⽽睇唔到旗⼿fing 緊咩旗，好彩有排⼿⾜爬住電燈柱睇旗⼿指示安排。<br />\n\r<br />\n我望住啲⼤廈外牆忽發奇想，如果有⼀枝強⼒電筒，再加幾張有啲字嘅剪影嘅卡紙，咪可以project 落啲⼤廈牆⾝囉<br />\r\n（即係好似要蝙蝠俠出動果陣有枝⼤射燈咁），咁arm 今⽇⾒有個post 介紹⼤⼤枝電筒可以加攻加防，所以想brainstorm 下work 唔work<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n優：可以好多⼈同⼀時間睇到，唔使⼈傳⼈。都算易帶出街，唔怕俾狗咬啩<br />\n\r<br />\n缺點： 要晚上同有⼤廈牆⾝先work (但次次打⼤佬都係夜晚咁滯）換唔同嘅字可能會麻煩（但⼈傳⼈個時間可能仲耐？）可能中途會冇電<br />\n\r<br />\n⼤家點睇？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7FOG8s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7FOG8s.png&h=3bcf2936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0JQa1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0JQa1O.png&h=9967176b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WcdTe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WcdTe9.png&h=08251d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oT38G8w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoT38G8w.png&h=855d72c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tWE0yfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWE0yfc.png&h=54f2cb69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ffabbb50527f6202f41c70d79858e5aaf6863cb","tid":1383507,"uid":264753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}